title: For Sale:  WINCHESTER MODEL 1892 - .32-20 - MANUF 1908 - C&R
postcontent: For sale is a BEAUTIFUL 1892 Winchester rifle was manufactured in 1908. It bears serial number 444982. It has a 24" octagon barrel with good overall bore. The finish on the gun is good, with some discoloring on the top of the bolt. The rifle functions flawlessly. It makes a beautiful sound when it is racked, hammer stays back, fires with a nice and crisp trigger. Also has a half-cock safety. The stock is the prettiest I have seen on a 100+ year old rifle.
